                     <interp inst="t18240603-19-person234" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am an officer. I took the prisoner, who was running with the cask - I saw him stopped.</p>
               <p>(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
               <p>Prisoner. I throw myself on the mercy of the Court, having been out of work for a long time.</p>
               <p>GUILTY. Aged 23.</p>
